{"tid":2373574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指 : 特朗普正與盟友商討成立新政黨，並計劃命名為「愛國黨」!","createTime":"2021-01-20T14:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T14:56:43.000Z","uid":219007,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"307c98561a48aa654c1b0957f22839bcd86e1683","tid":2373574,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"即將卸任的美國總統特朗普似乎未有打算退下火線。《華爾街日報》引述消息指，特朗普正與盟友商討成立新政黨，並計劃命名為「愛國黨」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普多次聲稱大選涉舞弊、攻擊共和黨人，再加上國會衝突，他與共和黨的分歧越見明顯，不少共和黨黨員及其前內閣成員紛紛與他「割蓆」，最新傳出是共和黨資深參議員麥康奈爾表明特朗普煽動其支持者於 1 月 6 日衝擊國會，應該受譴責。<br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，特朗普似乎未有計劃退出政壇，反而正積極考慮籌組新政黨，繼續參與美國政事。報道引述消息人士說，特朗普上周跟數名團隊成員及其他人談及組新黨的問題，並已想好名稱，叫 Patriot Party （愛國黨）。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，在近日的民調中，特朗普仍然得到共和黨選民的強大支持。特朗普周二 (19/1) 發表告別演說，並表示任期雖即將結束，但「運動才剛開始。」 然而，籌組新政黨須動用到大量人力及財力，報道指現時仍未清楚特朗普的計劃會否落實。<br />\n<br />\n美國政壇長期由民主黨和共和黨主導，過往其他黨派難以在選舉中取得足夠支持成為有威脅的第三股勢力。共和黨內部相信也不會支持特朗普分走支持者、進一步削弱共和黨支持者數量的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%B5%84%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8-%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E9%BB%A8/?fbclid=IwAR32PceGIEzPIOfwSKV-VlssH-Cp2Ivenx0ZWW0DKQI8AvhQUjOg7_miUiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25BB%25A8%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32PceGIEzPIOfwSKV-VlssH-Cp2Ivenx0ZWW0DKQI8AvhQUjOg7_miUiY&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=55918173\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25BB%25A8%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32PceGIEzPIOfwSKV-VlssH-Cp2Ivenx0ZWW0DKQI8AvhQUjOg7_miUiY&h=c928b441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%B5%84%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8-%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E9%BB%A8/?fbclid=IwAR32PceGIEzPIOfwSKV-VlssH-Cp2Ivenx0ZWW0DKQI8AvhQUjOg7_miUiY</a>"},{"pid":"12b2e56cc731fac375ab0e77d3b6ee39497a47cf","tid":2373574,"uid":171788,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"𠝹共和黨票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ce2fc63fcc459d39c84272b8fbf7ba980dac04","tid":2373574,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:21:20.000Z","msg":"美國兩黨制行之已久，我唔覺得一個侵侵可以剽到第三勢力出嚟囉<br />\n你估香港本土派咩"},{"pid":"2909b45ca16160bb92cb2015c247952927e0e777","tid":2373574,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"大前提係要<br />\n<br />\n1. 民主黨要遵守遊戲規則<br />\n2. 企業要遵守遊戲規則<br />\n3. 左膠要覺醒後遵守遊戲規則<br />\n4. 侵之後冇俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n否則冇撚用同香港民主黨話要繼續議會戰線一樣拉撚圾"},{"pid":"e79069e6f68c87133f7410d38997d0fccb643f53","tid":2373574,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"估計係拖住想彈劾佢D叛徒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n那個敢反叛, 派親信同佢玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dd6c0a67bada7e36ab2dd276bf949ac859782c","tid":2373574,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"啲譯名咁似 愛港力 呢D"},{"pid":"1e36b367ec89f9c727c097449558b80dea9d5b1a","tid":2373574,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"香港去左美國果d 可以入黨"},{"pid":"5bb58276f0badacca5946db6fb4f3ebc5f4deb68","tid":2373574,"uid":1769